                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The plated python has a creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed]</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The plated python begins its turn</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The python's breath seeps into the grabbed creature. That creature must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:32] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature's body hardens and stiffens, causing it to become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Petrified] for 1 round and Swallowed Whole.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is petrified permanently and Swallowed Whole.</p>"
                },
